<!-- Content Section -->
<section class="content-section">
    <h2>Please Join Us</h2>
    <p>
        We are Ali Al-Rasheed and Asmaa Al-Hassan, third-year students at the Faculty of Informatics Engineering.
        We are currently interns at Medad Organization as part of the "1000 Programmers" project, specializing in ASP.NET Core + Angular.
